rComments: This teacher is so hot it made taking the class totally worth it.  Since there are no exams and the lecture notes are posted online, you don't even have to take notes when you're sitting in class...just show up, write a few papers and a book review, and that's all.

Not a very interesting class but very very easy. No exams so there is no need to buy the textbook or course pack. Quizzes are very easy and entirely from lecture material. Boring sometimes but hey, it's an A.
